Ok, I'm not really sure who's at this Pred civil war battle, so if I 
shoot at someone nonexistant, please ignore it.

(I can't really think to clearly with this hangover)

::Killfest/Scyther/Demise/EndBringer/Goldeneye/Darkmouse::

Killfest glances up to see a lightning bolt, ignoring it and keeping 
his mind on the battle.

"Lets finish this battle and get back to base afterwards. The mission 
can wait," he replies, throwing Aerostreak away and firing two 
missiles after him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther swirls out of the way of some shots, firing a charge down at 
Akron.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Darkmouse looks down at the ground. She didn't like being carried by 
someone she couldn't see.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Back at the Predacon (council) base, rocks fly apart as Demise 
smashes through the ground, emerging in front of the door. He checks 
his scanners. A battle was raging several miles away.

He limps into the base, heading for the CR chambers.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
EndBringer roars, firing more missiles at Tankorr.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Goldeneye jerks her leg away as one of the energonians tries to grab 
it, firing back at the energonian.
